"4  (8-ounce) bone-in center-cut pork chops (about 1 inch thick)","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1 teaspoon canola oil","  Cooking spray","1  (8-ounce) container refrigerated prechopped onion (about 1 3/4 cups)","2 cups water","1/4 cup firmly packed brown sugar","1 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1/2 teaspoon ground cloves","1/2 teaspoon ground ginger","1  (5-ounce) package dried apples"